Class GFFParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.charite.compbio.jannovar.impl.parse.gtfgff.GFFParser

  • public class GFFParser
extends Object
    A class for parsing a stream of GFFRecord objects from a GTF or GFF file. This class is state-ful and not thread safe.

    Manuel Holtgrewe
